<text><body>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb ed="F" n="0118a16"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="1"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="1"><cb:jhead>大王觀世音經一卷</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="F" n="0118a17"/><cb:div><p xml:id="pF01p0118a1701"><note n="0118a1701" resp="CBETA" type="add">佛【CB】，<unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a1701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">佛</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>說觀世音<note n="0118a1702" resp="CBETA" type="add">經一卷【CB】，<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a1702"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">經一卷</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear></rdg></app><note n="0118a1703" resp="CBETA" type="add">讀誦【CB】，<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a1703"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">讀誦</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>千遍得度苦難拔除生死罪觀世音菩薩南无佛佛國有緣佛法相因
<lb ed="F" n="0118a18"/><note n="0118a1801" resp="CBETA" type="add">常樂【CB】，<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a1801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">常樂</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>我<note n="0118a1802" resp="CBETA" type="add">淨【CB】，<unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a1802"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">淨</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>　<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><note n="0118a1803" resp="CBETA" type="add">南无摩訶波若【CB】，<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a1803"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">南无摩訶波若</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>是大神呪　南无摩訶波若是大明呪　南无摩訶波若是大
<lb ed="F" n="0118a19"/><unclear></unclear>等等呪　<note n="0118a1901" resp="CBETA" type="add">淨光祕密佛【CB】，<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a1901"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">淨光祕密佛</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>　<note n="0118a1902" resp="CBETA" type="add">法藏【CB】，<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a1902"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">法藏</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>佛　師子吼神足遊王佛　告須弥登王佛　法護佛　金剛
<lb ed="F" n="0118a20"/><note n="0118a2001" resp="CBETA" type="add">藏師【CB】，<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a2001"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">藏師</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>子游戲佛　藥師瑠璃<note n="0118a2002" resp="CBETA" type="add">光【CB】，<unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a2002"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">光</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>佛　普光功德山王佛　善住功德寶王佛　六方六佛名号　東
<lb ed="F" n="0118a21"/>方寶光月<note n="0118a2101" resp="CBETA" type="add">殿【CB】，<unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a2101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">殿</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>妙尊音王佛　南方樹根華王佛　西方<note n="0118a2102" resp="CBETA" type="add">皂【CB】，<unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a2102"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">皂</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>王神通<note n="0118a2103" resp="CBETA" type="add">焰【CB】，艶【房山】</note><app n="0118a2103"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">焰</lem><rdg wit="【房山】">艶</rdg></app>華王佛　北方月殿清淨佛
<lb ed="F" n="0118a22"/>　上方无數精進寶首佛　下方善寂月音王佛　釋迦牟<g ref="#CB00112"/>佛　弥勒佛　中央一切眾生在此
<lb ed="F" n="0118a23"/><note n="0118a2301" resp="CBETA" type="add">世【CB】，<unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a2301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">世</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>界中者行住於地上及<note n="0118a2302" resp="CBETA" type="add">在虛空中慈憂【CB】，<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>【房山】</note><app n="0118a2302"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">在虛空中慈憂</lem><rdg wit="【房山】"><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear></rdg></app>於一切令各安休息晝夜脩治心常應誦此經消伏於</p></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>